headline: Alphabet & Tesla earnings, existing home sales: What to Watch
summary: Asking for a Trend host Josh Lipton takes a look at the top stories for investors to watch on Wednesday, July 23. In the afternoon, earnings results will be posted for Alphabet (GOOG, GOOGL), Tesla (TSLA), IBM (IBM), T-Mobile (TMUS), Chipotle (CMG), and Alaska Air (ALK). In the morning, existing home sales data for June will be published. Economists are expecting the number to fall slightly. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Asking for a Trend here.
